0. get files together
1. ghdl -s subFile.hdl subFile.hdl testerFile.hdl
    -- syntax check
2. ghdl -a subFile.hdl subFile.hdl testerFile.hdl
    -- analyze design
3. ghdl -e testerFile
    -- build executable

4. ghdl -r testerFile --vcd=output.vcd --stop-time=100us
    -- runs program, dumping simulated waveforms into file "output.vcd"

5. use gtkwave app to display waveform